<!DOCTYPE suite SYSTEM "https://testng.org/testng-1.0.dtd">
<suite name="Smoke Suite" verbose="1">
    <test name="Smoke Test">
        <packages>
            <package name="myapp.tests.smoketests"></package>
        </packages>
    </test>
</suite>


<!-- NOTES:
    1. xml files are used to RUN existing test cases
    2. xml file can be used to run test at any level=> suite > test > packages > groups > classes > methods
    3. verbose is OPTIONAL => it is only the amount of info that you see on the console after the test run
    4. SAVE THE XML FILE FIRST, then run it
    5. If the path is not correct, we see 'No Tests were found' error

-->